text: Interstate 785 (I-785) is an auxiliary Interstate Highway in the city of Greensboro in the U.S. state of North Carolina. Its south end is at I-40, I-85, and I-840. Its north end is at I-840 and U.S. Route 29 (US 29). The highway is long. The highway is a part of the Greensboro Urban Loop. In the future, the highway will go from Greensboro to Danville, Virginia. The highway will be around long. ==References== 785
